Package CS509.client.flight

Class Flight

java.lang.Object
CS509.client.flight.Flight
public class Flight extends Object
This class holds values pertaining to a single flight from one airport to another. Class member attributes are the same as defined by the CS509 server API and store values after conversion from XML received from the server to Java primitives. Attributes are accessed via getter and setter methods.
